%spark
val csvData = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", true).option("inferSchema", true).load("data/data_engineering.csv")

println("total rows: " + csvData.count())
csvData.show(10)
csvData.createOrReplaceTempView("ingestion_view")

%spark.sql
